Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那你怎么来了  -我也工作不要命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Why did you come in? - I work too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's boiling in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8毫伦琴  是泄露吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eight milliroentgen. A leak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然早响了  是外面飘进来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It would've gone off before. It's coming from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Americans?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碘131\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Iodine 131.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是军用  是铀衰变  铀235\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not military. It's uranium decay, U-235.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应堆燃料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Reactor fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是伊格纳利纳  离我们大概240公里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ignalina. Maybe, uh, 240 kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是乌拉娜·霍缪克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, this is Ulana Khomyuk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是白俄罗斯核能...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with the Institute of Nuclear En--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Looking for--?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好吧  冷静点  -别叫我冷静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- All right, stay calm. - Don't tell me to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们那儿才4毫伦琴  不是他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're at four. It's not them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来最近的是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's the next closest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利  但那不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's Chernobyl, but that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们离我们400公里呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're 400 kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么远不会有8毫伦琴飘过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's too far for eight milliroentgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非是反应堆暴露在外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'd have to be split open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他们知情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe they know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-碘片  -会是废料倾倒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Iodine. - Could it be a waste dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该有其他同位素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'd be seeing other isotopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核测试  新式炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nuclear test? Uh, new kind of bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们肯定能听说  这里半数人就干这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'd have heard. That's what half our people work on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是太空计划  卫星什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something with the space program like a satellite or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人接听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No one's answering the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给所有人打点滴  -点滴不够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get everyone started on an IV. - We don't have enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就儿童优先  -那也不够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- All the children then. - But we don't have enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就有多少打多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As many as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-老头子呢  -他在16室设立了烧伤病房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Where's the old man? - He's set up a burn ward in 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么呢  那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶  是牛奶  比水好使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Milk. It's milk. Much better than water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  快停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, no. Stop. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你干什么  -这是辐射烧伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What are you doing? - These are radiation burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的衣服都污染了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Their clothes are contaminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都脱掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get it all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're taking it down to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是切尔诺贝利的消防员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was a firefighter from Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能别推了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you stop pushing, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have our orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-回去吧  -抓住他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Disperse! - Hey, there! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么不让我们进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why you keeping us out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫教授\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Professor Legasov?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还没到时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还在处理其他事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're finishing up some other business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得要几分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It'll be a few more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-要给您端点茶吗  -不了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Can I get you some tea? - No, I'm fine. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您等的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you care to read
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看看谢比纳副主席的报告吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Deputy Chairman Shcherbina's report while you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Certainly. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  教授  你可以进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, Professor. They're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫教授\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Professor Legasov?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会支持你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢各位为本委员会尽责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you all for your duty to this commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先听取谢比纳副主席的报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We will begin with Deputy Chairman Shcherbina's briefing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  如有必要  再讨论接下来的行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then we will discuss next steps if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  总书记同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, comrade General Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴地汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm pleased to report
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利的情况已稳定了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that the situation in Chernobyl is stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军事和平民巡逻队已确保了当地安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Military and civilian patrols have secured the region,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡洛夫大将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Colonel General Pikalov,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,率领着专业处理化学性公害的军队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who commands troops specializing in chemical hazards,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也已被派遣到核电站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has been dispatched to the plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就辐射而言  核电站厂长布卡诺夫报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In terms of radiation, plant director Bryukhanov
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辐射量不超过3.6伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}reports no more than 3.6 roentgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被告知辐射量相当于一次胸透\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm told it's the equivalent of a chest X-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果你很久没做体检了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So if you're overdue for a check-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-外国媒体呢  -毫不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- And foreign press? - Totally unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克格勃第一副主席佘考夫向我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}KGB First Deputy Chairman Charkov assures me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已成功保护了我方安全利益\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that we have successfully protected our security interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们已经控制了局势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it seems like it's well in hand, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没其他事的话  休会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if there's nothing else, meeting adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能休会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, we can't adjourn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是库尔恰托夫研究所的列加索夫教授\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Professor Legasov of the Kurchatov Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授  你有疑问的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Professor, if you have any concerns,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以晚点跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}feel free to address them with me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  抱歉  很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't. I am sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三页  人员伤亡部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Page three, the section on casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"一位消防员在反应堆厂房外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"A fireman was severely burned on his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被地上一大块表面光滑的黑色矿物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"By a chunk of smooth, black mineral on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严重烫伤了手"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}outside the reactor building."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表面光滑的黑色矿物  是石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Smooth, black mineral-- graphite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上有石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's-There's graphite on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了水箱爆炸  导致现场有碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, there was a... A tank explosion. There's debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那能有多重要...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of what importance that could be--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个核电站只有一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's only one place in the entire facility
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有石墨  那就是堆芯里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where you will find graphite: inside the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果外面地上有石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If there's graphite on the ground outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就意味着爆炸的不是控制系统水箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it means it wasn't a control system tank that exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是反应堆芯  它被炸开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was the reactor core. It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢比纳同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, Comrade Shcherbina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总书记同志  我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrade General Secretary, I can assure you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫教授弄错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that Professor Legasov is mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布卡诺夫说反应堆芯完好无损\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bryukhanov reports that the reactor core is intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-至于辐射量...  -没错  3.6伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- And as for the radiation-- - Yes, 3.6 roentgen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说一下  这并不等于一次胸透的辐射量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which, by the way, is not the equivalent of one chest X-ray,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是相当于四百次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but rather 400 chest X-rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不是因为这个原因感到不安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That number's been bothering me for a different reason, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是低精度剂量计的量程上限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's also the maximum reading on low-limit dosimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只上报了手里有的数值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They gave us the number they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为真正的数值远比那高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think the true number is much, much higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没弄错  这位消防员手中拿着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If I'm right, this fireman was holding the equivalent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当于四百万次胸透的辐射量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of four million chest X-rays in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫教授  不要危言耸听  歇斯底里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Professor Legasov, there's no place for alarmist hysteria--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是事实  就不是危言耸听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not alarmist if it's a fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全没听到什么事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I don't hear any facts at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只听到一个我不认识的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All I hear is a man I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妄加臆测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}engaging in conjecture
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且所说的与党官员所报告的内容截然相反\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in direct contradiction to what has been reported by party officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm, uh... I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't mean, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否允许我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, may I express my concern
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静且尊敬地表达我的担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as calmly and as respectfully as I--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-列加索夫教授  -鲍里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Professor Legasov-- - Boris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I will allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RBMK反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}An RBMK reactor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用铀235作为燃料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}uses uranium 235 as fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:13:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铀235每个原子都像一颗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every atom of U-235 is like a bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以接近光速射出的子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}traveling at nearly the speed of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能穿透所经之处的一切事物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}penetrating everything in its path:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木头  金属  水泥  肉体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}woods, metal, concrete, flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一克铀235中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every gram of U-235 holds
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有10的21次方颗这种子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over a billion trillion of these bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一克而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's in one gram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而切尔诺贝利的装载量有三百多万克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Chernobyl holds over three million grams,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and right now, it is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放射性粒子会随风\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Winds will carry radioactive
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散布到整个大陆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}particles across the entire continent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后随着雨水降落到地面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}rain will bring them down on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是3乘10的27次方颗子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's three million billion trillion bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在...在我们的空气中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the... in the air we breathe,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饮水中  食物中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the water we drink, the food we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中大多数子弹会持续发射一百多年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Most of these bullets will not stop firing for 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而有些会持续五万年以上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some of them, not for 50,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你的顾虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, and, uh, this concern
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全基于报告中对一块石头的描述吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}stems entirely from the description of a rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢比纳同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrade Shcherbina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你去切尔诺贝利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to go to Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要亲自查看反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You take a look at the reactor, you personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后直接向我汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you report directly back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明智的决定  总书记同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A wise decision, comrade General Secretary--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带列加索夫教授一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And take Professor Legasov with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  总书记同志  但我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forgive me, comrade General Secretary, but I--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂得核反应堆的原理吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know how a nuclear reactor works?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不懂  -不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你怎么能理解你所看到的情况呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then how will you know what you're looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会议结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Meeting adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核反应堆的原理是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How does a nuclear reactor work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -这个问题很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What? - It's a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案一点也不简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's hardly a simple answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  你觉得我太笨了  听不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course, you presume I'm too stupid to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我换种说法  告诉我核反应堆的原理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I'll restate: tell me how a nuclear reactor works,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我就叫士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or I'll have one of these
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你扔出直升机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}soldiers throw you out of the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核反应堆利用蒸汽发电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A nuclear reactor makes electricity with steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒸汽推动汽轮机产生电能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The steam turns a turbine which generates electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常规发电厂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where a typical power plant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过烧煤来产生蒸汽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}makes steam by burning coal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而核电厂...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a nuclear plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核电厂中会利用裂变反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In a nuclear plant, we use something called fission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采用一种不稳定的元素  比如铀235\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We take an unstable element like uranium 235,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原子核中的中子数量过多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which has too many neutrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-中子就是...  -子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- A neutron is, uh-- - The bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹从铀核中射出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, bullets are flying off of the uranium.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果将足够多的铀原子聚集在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if we put enough uranium atoms close together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自一个原子的子弹最终会击中另一个原子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the bullets from one atom will eventually strike another atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞击产生的力量会使原子分裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The force of this impact splits that atom apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,释放出巨大的能量  这就是裂变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}releasing a tremendous amount of energy, fission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那石墨呢  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- And the graphite? - Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中子的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The neutrons are actually
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太快了  我们称之为"通量"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}traveling so fast-- we call this "flux"--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's relatively unlikely that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铀原子彼此击中的概率很低\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the uranium atoms will ever hit one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在RBMK反应堆中  燃料棒被石墨包围\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In RBMK reactors, we surround the fuel rods with graphite
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是调节  减慢中子通量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to moderate, slow down, the neutron flux.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白核反应堆的原理了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know how a nuclear reactor works.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不需要你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now I don't need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-帮帮我  我找不到我丈夫  -现在没空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Can you help me? I need to find my husband. - No. Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-米哈伊尔  -柳德米拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Mikhail! - Lyudmilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带她走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带她离开这里  拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take her away from here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离他们远点  你想生病吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get away from them! You want to get sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你带她离开  求求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please take her, please take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你带她离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please take her, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你带她离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please take her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我是瓦西里·伊格纳滕科的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me, I am Vasily Ignatenko's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是消防员  伊格纳滕科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's a fireman. Ignatenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳滕科  军事第六消防和救援站的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ignatenko, Sixth Paramilitary Fire and Rescue Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得找到他  求求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need to find him. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳滕科...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ignatenko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要被直升机转送去莫斯科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's being transported by helicopter to Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hospital number six.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  他不要紧吧  我能看他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why, is he all right? Can I see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想见他  那去莫斯科吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to see him? Go to Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们都不让我们离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But they're not letting us leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们布洛夫少校批准了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell them Major Burov allows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他们什么时候带他走  -现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh. When are they taking him? - Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在接近核电厂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're approaching the power plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What have they done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看见内部吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you see inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要  看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't have to. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房顶上就有石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's graphite on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个厂房都被炸开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The whole building's been blown open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆芯已经暴露了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The core's exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白你怎么从这儿就能断定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't see how you can tell that from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:19:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, for God's sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见那光晕了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at that glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是放射线离子化空气的结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's radiation ionizing the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼见才能为实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, if we can't see, we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-直接开到厂房上方去  -鲍里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get us directly over the building! - Boris,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不许直呼我名字  -如果我们飞到...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Don't you use my name! - if we fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露的反应堆上空  我们一周内就会死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...directly over an open reactor, we'll be dead within a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞到厂房上面去  否则我枪毙你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get us over that building, or I'll have you shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你直接飞到堆芯上方  我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you fly directly over that core, I promise you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上  你会巴不得被枪毙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by tomorrow morning, you'll be begging for that bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord1\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur8\fad(0,0)\pos(191.2,164.801)}明斯克  白俄罗斯共产党总部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你最好改天再来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps if you came back another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉宁副书记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Deputy Secretary Garanin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白俄罗斯核能源研究所的乌拉娜·霍缪克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ulana Khomyuk of the Byelorussian Institute for Nuclear Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来介绍一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me introduce--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为切尔诺贝利而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm here about Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈得太愉快了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Such a lovely time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-尽快再来吧  -我会的  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Visit again soon. - I will. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须告诉你  这就是大家不喜欢科学家的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I must tell you, this is why no one likes scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我们需要治好疾病时  他们跑哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When we have a disease to cure, where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在实验室  埋头苦读  于是老太太就死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In a lab, noses in their books, and so Grandma dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没事的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But when there isn't a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到处跑  散布恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they're everywhere, spreading fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道切尔诺贝利的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know about Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道堆芯部分或全部暴露在外了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know that the core is either partially or completely exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-鬼知道那什么意思  -如果你不立即\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Whatever that means. - And that if you don't immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发放碘片并组织撤离整座城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}issue iodine tablets and then evacuate this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数十万人会罹患癌症\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}hundreds of thousands of people are going to get cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而还不知道要死多少人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and God knows how many more will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利确实出了事故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There has been an accident at Chernobyl,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我被告知绝对没有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I've been assured there is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在告诉你有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm telling you that there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更倾向于我的意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I prefer my opinion to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是核物理学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a nuclear physicist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你成为副书记之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Before you were Deputy Secretary,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在一家鞋厂工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you worked in a shoe factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我之前确实在鞋厂工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I worked in a shoe factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在我说了算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now I'm in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"敬全世界的工人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"To the workers of the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碘片会避免你的甲状腺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stable iodine will keep your thyroid
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸收放射性碘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from absorbing radioactive iodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天服用一粒  直到吃完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take one a day for as long as they last.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且向东走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And go east.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离明斯克越远越好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get as far from Minsk as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得太过火了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's overkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡洛夫在炫耀  为了让我们难堪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pikalov's showing off to make us look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来怎么样不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It doesn't matter how it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢比纳是个纯粹的官僚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shcherbina is a pure bureaucrat,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他既顽固又愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as stupid as he is pigheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用最简单的语言把真相告诉他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll tell him the truth in the simplest terms possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡洛夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pikarov!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.76,0:24:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢比纳同志  总工程师福明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrade Shcherbina, Chief Engineer Fomin,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡洛夫大将和我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Colonel General Pikalov, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为您的莅临深感荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}are honored at your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.05,0:24:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常非常荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Deeply, deeply honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.75,0:24:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  对于在此情况下会面我们表示遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Naturally, we regret the circumstances of your visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.62,0:25:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如您所见  我们正在控制损失方面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but, as you can see, we are making excellent progress
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.81,0:25:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得卓越的进展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in containing the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.47,0:25:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经开始对事故原因进行调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have begun our own inquiry into the cause of the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.63,0:25:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是一张名单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I have a list of individuals
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写着事故的相关责任人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who we believe are accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.66,0:25:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫教授  我听说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Professor Legasov, I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.67,0:25:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在说些危险的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you've been saying dangerous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.83,0:25:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very dangerous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.43,0:25:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说我们的堆芯爆炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Apparently, our reactor core exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.55,0:25:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我RBMK核反应堆堆芯怎么会爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, tell me how an RBMK reactor core explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.65,0:25:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还无法做出解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not prepared to explain it at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.63,0:25:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我所料  他不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As I presumed, he has no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.95,0:25:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可耻  真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's disgraceful, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.07,0:26:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时候散播虚假消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To spread disinformation at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.09,0:26:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么在楼顶上看到了石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why did I see graphite on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.54,0:26:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石墨只在堆芯里才有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Graphite is only found in the core,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.01,0:26:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被用作中子通量调节剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where it's used as a neutron flux moderator.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.54,0:26:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.98,0:26:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福明  为什么副主席在楼顶上看到了石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fomin, why did the Deputy Chairman see graphite on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.75,0:26:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that... that can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.45,0:26:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢比纳同志  抱歉  但是石墨...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrade Shcherbina, my apologies, but graphite...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.16,0:26:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.41,0:26:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你看到的是烧焦的混凝土\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps you saw burnt concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.67,0:26:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你就错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now there you made a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.70,0:26:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我可能不怎么懂核反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because I may not know much about nuclear reactors,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.50,0:26:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我对混凝土很了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I know a lot about concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.45,0:26:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-同志  我向你保证...  -我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Comrade, I assure you-- - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.08,0:26:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得列加索夫错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think Legasov is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.87,0:26:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么证明呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How shall we prove it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.06,0:26:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的大量程剂量计刚刚运到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our high-range dosimeter just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.54,0:26:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以用铅屏蔽我们的一辆卡车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We could cover one of our trucks with lead shielding,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.71,0:26:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把剂量计装在前面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}mount the dosimeter on the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.73,0:27:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你的手下尽可能接近火灾现场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have one of your men get as close to the fire as he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.99,0:27:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他足够多的保护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give him every bit of protection you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.75,0:27:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但记住  就算有铅屏蔽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But understand that even with lead shielding,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.03,0:27:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能还是不够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it may not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.85,0:27:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就自己去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.36,0:27:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.10,0:29:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.88,0:29:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是3伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not three roentgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.24,0:29:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是15000伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's 15,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.08,0:29:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢比纳同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrade Shcherbina--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.81,0:30:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个数值意味着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does that number mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.15,0:30:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着堆芯炸开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It means the core is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.80,0:30:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着我们肉眼可见的火灾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It means the fire we're watching with our own eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.04,0:30:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比广岛原子弹释放的辐射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is giving off nearly twice the radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.79,0:30:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高出将近两倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}released by the bomb in Hiroshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.57,0:30:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还是每个小时的量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that's every single hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.40,0:30:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小时接一小时  爆炸已经过了20小时了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hour after hour, 20 hours since the explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.45,0:30:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已是40颗原子弹的当量了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so 40 bombs worth by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.36,0:30:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天又再加48颗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forty-eight more tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.66,0:30:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且它不会停下  一周或一个月后都不会停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it will not stop. Not in a week, not in a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.48,0:30:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会一直燃烧  扩散有害物质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It will burn and spread its poison
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.03,0:30:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到整个大陆都完蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}until the entire continent is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.99,0:30:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请护送布卡诺夫同志和福明同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please escort Comrades Bryukhanov and Fomin
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.36,0:30:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到当地的党总部去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the local party headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.67,0:30:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢你们的服务  -同志...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thank you for your service. - Comrade--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.23,0:30:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可以走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.44,0:30:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是迪亚特洛夫负责的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dyatlov was in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.60,0:30:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是迪亚特洛夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was Dyatlov!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.27,0:30:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-告诉我怎么扑灭  -我们用直升机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Tell me how to put it out. - We'll use helicopters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.03,0:30:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像灭林火那样浇水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll drop water on it like a forest fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.05,0:30:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  你不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no. You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.02,0:30:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是火灾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.58,0:30:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个裂变中的反应堆堆芯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a fissioning reactor core
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.33,0:30:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以超过两千度的高温燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}burning at over 2,000 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.54,0:30:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热量会瞬间将水汽化...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The heat will instantly vaporize the water--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.30,0:30:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们如何扑灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do we put it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.68,0:31:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所面临的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are dealing with something
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.72,0:31:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星球上从没发生过的灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that has never occurred on this planet before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.25,0:31:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boron.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.76,0:31:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硼和沙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boron and sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.11,0:31:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管那会产生其他的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that'll create problems of its own,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.63,0:31:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我...我不知道还有什么办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I-I don't see any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.21,0:31:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  需要成千上万次的投放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course, it's going to take thousands of drops,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.97,0:31:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你不能把直升机开到堆芯正上方去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because you can't fly the helicopters directly over the core,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.69,0:31:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有多数投放物会偏离目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so most of it is going to miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.22,0:31:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-要多少硼和沙子  -我没法...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How much sand and boron? - Well, I can't be--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.81,0:31:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-老天  大概就行了  -五千吨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- For God's sake, roughly! - Five thousand tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.92,0:31:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  显然我们要疏散一大片区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And obviously, we're going to need to evacuate an enormous area--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.59,0:31:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管那个  集中精力灭火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Never mind that. Focus on the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.39,0:31:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在集中精力灭火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am focusing on the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.36,0:31:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风正卷着所有的烟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The wind, it's carrying all that smoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.58,0:31:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的放射性物质扩散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all that radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.47,0:31:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少疏散普里皮亚季  离这儿只有三公里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At least evacuate Pripyat. It's three kilometers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.40,0:31:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那事由我决定  -那就决定吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That's my decision to make. - Then make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.69,0:31:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我被命令不能疏散  -你到底是不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I've been told not to. - Is it or is not--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.03,0:31:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm in charge here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.18,0:31:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你只和我讲你明白的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This will go much easier if you talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.78,0:31:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不要谈你不明白的事的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the things you do understand
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.97,0:31:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一切都会简单得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and not about the things you do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.74,0:32:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.32,0:32:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去给你调五千吨沙袋和硼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to get you 5,000 tons of sand and boron.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.96,0:32:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有家酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.74,0:33:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想用那个杯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd prefer one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.72,0:33:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是迷信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Superstitious?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.75,0:33:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯科来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Moscow?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.80,0:33:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是为火灾来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you here because of the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.45,0:33:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么我们需要担心的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anything we should be worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.34,0:33:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.11,0:35:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord1\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur8\fad(0,0)\pos(191.2,83.2)}4月27日  上午\N\N\N\N\N{\fs20}爆炸发生30小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.16,0:35:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就位了  接近投放点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're in position. Approaching drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.54,0:35:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clear to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.04,0:35:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到  我们会一架一架地轮流投放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Copy. We'll go one by one in rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.43,0:35:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提醒他们注意距离限制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remind them about the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.98,0:35:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不能直接飞到火焰上方去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They cannot fly directly over the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.10,0:35:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少保持10米距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A minimum of a ten-meter perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.52,0:35:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10米距离  收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ten meter perimeter. Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.23,0:35:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L1  准备投放  至少10米距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lead one, err preflight, maintain minimum ten-meter perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.28,0:35:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.28,0:35:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40米...35米...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forty meters... 35...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.24,0:35:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30米...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}30...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.08,0:35:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  他们飞得太近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, no! They're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.54,0:35:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不能飞到火焰上方  那要怎么...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They can't get over the fire. How are they supposed--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.33,0:35:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能让风吹过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The wind will have to carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.17,0:35:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们  他们不能飞到堆芯上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell them, they cannot go over the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.34,0:35:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L1太近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lead One is too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.76,0:35:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重复一遍  他们太近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I repeat, they are too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.43,0:35:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.35,0:36:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L1  你已经飞进危险距离内了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lead One, you are inside the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.68,0:36:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有收到  信号不良\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did not copy. Signal's breaking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.61,0:36:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lead One?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.36,0:36:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.86,0:36:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L1  你收到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lead One, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.28,0:36:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L1  请回话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lead One, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.90,0:36:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收到了吗  L1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you copy, Lead One?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.86,0:36:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lead One!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.69,0:36:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  我怎么指挥其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir? What do I tell the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.57,0:36:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的办法吗  列加索夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there any other way, Legasov?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.08,0:36:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派下一架飞机进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Send the next one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.50,0:36:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们从西边靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell them to approach from the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.79,0:37:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord1\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur8\fad(0,2100)\pos(191.2,97.601)}莫斯科  库尔恰托夫原子能研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.52,0:37:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库尔恰托夫原子能研究所第四实验室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kurchatov Institute Laboratory Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.36,0:37:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜·古泽斯卡亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Marina Gruzinskaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.42,0:37:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是明斯克的乌拉娜·霍缪克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's Ulana Khomyuk from Minsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.74,0:37:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  你能打电话来真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yes, how nice of you to phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.37,0:37:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们很久没联系了  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's been too long. - It has.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.79,0:37:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打电话是想问问我们的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was actually calling about our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.17,0:37:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就是在乡下的那个  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You know, the one in the country. - Oh, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.92,0:37:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问问他现在怎么样  那里现在好热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted to see how he's doing. It's so hot there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.21,0:37:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  非常热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, it's extremely hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.76,0:37:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他的侄子们正要飞过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but his nephews are flying down,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.38,0:37:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们总是可以让天气凉爽下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they always bring cool weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.34,0:37:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  哪个侄子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh? Which nephews?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.76,0:37:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs16\bord1\blur5\fn微软雅黑\fad(0,0)\b0\pos(374,247)}暗指元素硅[Si]和硼[Bo]\N分别排在元素周期表的第14位和第5位
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.76,0:37:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西姆卡  14岁  小鲍里斯  5岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Simka, who's 14, and little Boris, who's five.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.77,0:37:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.23,0:38:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过孩子爬在你身上时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Though children can make you even hotter
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.06,0:38:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你觉得更热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when they're crawling all over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.77,0:38:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我应该去看看他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe I should visit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.27,0:38:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  他们不欢迎访客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, they don't want visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我得回去工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry, um, I have to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.49,0:38:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在很忙  再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's very busy right now. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.83,0:38:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在往火上投放沙子和硼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're dropping sand and boron on the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.20,0:38:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我也会那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.58,0:38:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我想也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I'm sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.32,0:38:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.33,0:38:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都很顺利  二十次投放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been smooth. Twenty drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.13,0:39:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.46,0:39:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市有五万人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are 50,000 people in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.18,0:39:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊林教授  委员会成员之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Professor Ilyin, who's also on the commission,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.60,0:39:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说这点辐射用不着疏散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}says the radiation isn't high enough to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.27,0:39:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊林不是物理学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ilyin isn't a physicist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.31,0:39:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, he's a medical doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.48,0:39:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他说安全  那就安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If he says it's safe, it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.19,0:39:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们留在这儿就不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not if they stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.66,0:39:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.77,0:39:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  所以我们活不过五年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we are, and we'll be dead in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.99,0:39:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.58,0:39:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.37,0:40:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是谢比纳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shcherbina.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.22,0:40:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.85,0:40:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞典的一座核电站检测到了辐射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A nuclear plant in Sweden has detected radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.81,0:40:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并分辨出是我们燃料的副产品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and identified it as a byproduct of our fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.94,0:40:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国人拍了卫星照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Americans took satellite photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.65,0:40:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应堆建筑  烟雾  还有火灾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The reactor building, the smoke, the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.74,0:41:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界都知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The whole world knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.17,0:41:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风一直吹向德国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The wind has been blowing toward Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.13,0:41:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法兰克福  已经禁止孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're not letting children play outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.59,0:41:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去外面玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.62,0:41:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想抽烟吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Want a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.29,0:41:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏联境内发生了一起核事故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There has been a nuclear accident in the Soviet Union
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.67,0:41:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏联也承认消息属实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the Soviets have admitted that it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.54,0:41:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏联方面称\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Soviet version is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.03,0:41:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}核事故
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.30,0:41:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基辅市附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One of the atomic reactors
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.63,0:41:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利核电站内一处反应堆受损\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at the Chernobyl Atomic Power Plant near the city of Kiev was damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.95,0:42:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯科有推断称\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and there is speculation in Moscow
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.93,0:42:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能已有人受伤甚至死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that people were injured and may have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.68,0:42:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏联如此痛快地承认了事故的发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Soviets may have been fairly quick to acknowledge the accident
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.12,0:42:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur0\fad(3200,3200)\pos(192,58.667)}4月27日  下午2点\N\N\N\N\N{\fs20}爆炸发生36小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.43,0:42:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因为证据已以轻微核辐射的形式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because evidence in the form of mild nuclear radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.85,0:42:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越了苏联边界  到达斯堪的纳维亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}had already reached beyond the Soviet borders to Scandinavia.
