Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.61,0:46:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了掉头  这里是禁区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I said turn around. This is a restricted zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.24,0:46:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来自白俄罗斯核能源研究所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm from the Byelorussian Institute for Nuclear Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.74,0:46:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有许可吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you have permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.66,0:46:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  事情紧急  我得找人谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen to me, I need to speak to someone urgently.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.12,0:46:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上掉头  要不然我就逮捕你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turn around right now, or I'll arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.37,0:46:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要逮捕我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you arrest me,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.41,0:46:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就带我去见最高负责人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you should take me to the highest possible authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.05,0:46:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要展开放射性调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have to start a radiological survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.55,0:46:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个区一个区的来  徒步  手持剂量仪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sector by sector, on foot, dosimeters in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.60,0:46:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.69,0:47:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.36,0:47:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrades--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.73,0:47:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警卫在南部检查点逮捕了这个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The guards arrested this woman at the south checkpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.48,0:47:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本该把她关进牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd have put her in a cell--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.19,0:47:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他觉得你们应该知道我都知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But he thought you should know that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.70,0:47:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们的反应堆芯爆炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know that your reactor core is exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.03,0:47:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道石墨着火了  燃料正在熔化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know the graphite is on fire, the fuel is melting,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.49,0:47:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你们在反应堆上方投放沙子和硼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you're dropping sand and boron on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.58,0:47:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可能觉得这很明智  但你们犯了个错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which you probably thought was smart, but you've made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.87,0:47:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌拉娜·尤里伊芙娜·霍缪克  首席物理学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ulana Yuriyvna Khomyuk, Chief Physicist,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.13,0:47:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就职于白俄罗斯核能源研究所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Byelorussian Institute for Nuclear Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.38,0:47:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是瓦列利·阿列克谢维奇·列加索夫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you are Valery Alexeyevich Legasov?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.92,0:47:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖堆芯的确能灭火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Smothering the core will put the fire out,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.43,0:47:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最终  温度还是会增加到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the temperature will eventually increase--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.26,0:47:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Believe me, I'm perfectly aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.43,0:47:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我估计至少需要一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I estimate at least a month
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.98,0:47:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆芯才会熔穿下部的混凝土层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before it melts through the lower concrete pad,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.06,0:47:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这能给我们时间  -不  没有一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- which gives us time-- - No, you don't have a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.94,0:47:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约只有两天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have approximately two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.73,0:47:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  燃料需要一个月的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, the fuel would take a month
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.90,0:47:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能到达这里的混凝土层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to reach the concrete pad here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.70,0:47:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是首先  在周二之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But first... it's going to burn through
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.70,0:47:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会熔穿这里的生物屏障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the biological shield here by Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.24,0:48:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦熔穿  燃料就会进入这些水箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when it does, it's going to hit these tanks--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.08,0:48:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起泡池  蓄水池\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}bubbler pools, reservoirs--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.62,0:48:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应急冷却系统的蓄水池  我理解你的担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Reservoirs for the ECS. I understand your concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.00,0:48:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我得到了工厂员工的证实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I confirmed it with plant personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.75,0:48:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-水箱基本上都空了  -不  之前是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- The tanks are nearly empty. - No, they were nearly empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.51,0:48:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有这些点  这里  这里  还有这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Each of these points here, here, and here
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.97,0:48:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将水排放至起泡池\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all drain to the bubbler pools.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.10,0:48:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜核电站里的管道应该已经全部破裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm guessing that every pipe in the building ruptured.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.76,0:48:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上我来时看到的那些消防车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then there are those fire engines that I saw on the way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.89,0:48:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消防软管还连着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The fire hoses are still connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.77,0:48:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一直都在向建筑物喷水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They've been gushing water into the structure this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.61,0:48:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水箱是满的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The tanks are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.65,0:48:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水箱是满的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The tanks are full.
