Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.06,0:48:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs16\b1\bord1\blur5\shad0\3c&H2A5342&\pos(192.6,248)\c&HD3D3D3&}切尔诺贝利核电站发生了一起事故
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.61,0:48:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs16\b1\bord1\blur5\shad0\3c&H2A5342&\pos(192.6,248)\c&HD3D3D3&}一处核反应堆受损
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.90,0:48:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs16\b1\bord1\blur5\shad0\3c&H2A5342&\pos(192.6,248)\c&HD3D3D3&}目前正在采取措施解决事故带来的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.65,0:48:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs16\b1\bord1\blur5\shad0\3c&H2A5342&\pos(192.6,248)\c&HD3D3D3&}受害群众得到了援助
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.37,0:48:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs16\b1\bord1\blur5\shad0\3c&H2A5342&\pos(192.6,248)\c&HD3D3D3&}政府已成立委员会调查
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.69,0:49:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有十分钟时间  然后又得接着打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have ten minutes, then I'm back on the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.99,0:49:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向所有的友国致歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}apologizing to our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.99,0:49:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我们的敌国致歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}apologizing to our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.29,0:49:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的力量取决于自我认知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our power comes from the perception of our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.21,0:49:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们明白这次事故造成了多大损失吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you understand the damage this has done?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.38,0:49:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们明白这事关多么重大吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you understand what's at stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.09,0:49:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲍里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boris.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.68,0:49:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫教授将进行汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Professor Legasov will deliver our briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.68,0:49:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There is some good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.48,0:49:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空投在有效地减小火势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The air drops are working to douse the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.15,0:49:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放射性核素排放量也有所减少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's been a reduction in radionuclide emissions,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.94,0:49:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但火还要至少两周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the fire will not be extinguished
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.74,0:49:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能被灭掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for at least another two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.70,0:50:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外还有一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There is also an additional problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.12,0:50:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核燃料就算没着火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nuclear fuel doesn't turn cold
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.91,0:50:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会冷却下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}simply because it is not on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.79,0:50:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  其温度有可能会上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In fact, the temperature will likely rise
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.33,0:50:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们投放了一层沙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as a result of the blanket of sand we've dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.42,0:50:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铀会熔化沙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The uranium will melt the sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.13,0:50:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成熔岩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}creating a kind of lava
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.93,0:50:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熔掉下面的保护屏障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which will begin to melt down through the shield below.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.05,0:50:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你制造了熔岩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have made lava?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.39,0:50:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这在预料之中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I anticipated this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.10,0:50:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以为有足够的时间来加固\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believed there was time to reinforce
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.31,0:50:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面的混凝土保护层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this lower concrete pad
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.65,0:50:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避免熔岩侵入地下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before the lava reached the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.07,0:50:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污染地下水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and contaminated the groundwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.94,0:50:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事实证明  我考虑错了方向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But as it turned out, I was worried about the wrong thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.87,0:50:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我本以为反应堆下面的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was my understanding that these large water tanks
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.58,0:50:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大型水箱几乎是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}under the reactor were essentially empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.29,0:50:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是白俄罗斯核能源研究所的乌拉娜·霍缪克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Ulana Khomyuk of the Byelorussian Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.42,0:50:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了她  我们意识到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks to her insight, we are now aware
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.67,0:50:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水箱现在其实是满的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that the tanks are, in fact, full.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.34,0:51:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装满了水而已  这有什么问题吗  教授\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of water. Why is that a problem, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.22,0:51:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当熔岩进入这些水箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When the lava enters these tanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.97,0:51:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水会立即过热并蒸发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it will instantly superheat and vaporize
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.89,0:51:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水箱一共有约七千立方米的水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}approximately 7,000 cubic meters of water,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.19,0:51:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会引起严重的热爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}causing a significant thermal explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.36,0:51:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How significant?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.03,0:51:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs16\bord1\blur5\fn微软雅黑\fad(0,0)\b0\pos(374,247)}相当于200到400万顿TNT炸药威力
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.03,0:51:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们估计约为{\u1}两到四百万吨级{\u0}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We estimate between two and four megatons.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.28,0:51:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半径三十公里内的所有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything within a 30-kilometer radius
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.99,0:51:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将被完全摧毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}will be completely destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.87,0:51:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括切尔诺贝利剩下的三个反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}including the three remaining reactors at Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.33,0:51:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而堆芯中的所有放射性物质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The entirety of the radioactive material in all of the cores
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.75,0:51:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将被喷射出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}will be ejected at force
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.17,0:51:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被巨大的冲击扩散开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and dispersed by a massive shock wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.34,0:51:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最远至大约两百公里外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which will extend approximately 200 kilometers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.51,0:51:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能对整个基辅地区及明斯克部分地区人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and likely be fatal to the entire population of Kiev
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.89,0:51:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造成致命性伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as well as a portion of Minsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.10,0:51:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核辐射的释放量非常巨大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The release of radiation will be severe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.98,0:52:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将影响整个苏联乌克兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and will impact all of Soviet Ukraine,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.36,0:52:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉脱维亚  立陶宛  白俄罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Latvia, Lithuania, Byelorussia,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.11,0:52:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及波兰  捷克斯洛伐克  匈牙利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as well as Poland, Czechoslovakia, Hungary,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.41,0:52:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗马尼亚和东德大部分地区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Romania, and most of East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.62,0:52:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么个影响法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean "impact"?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.33,0:52:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于大部分地区  几乎会永久破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For much of the area, a nearly permanent disruption
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.05,0:52:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食物和水的供应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of the food and water supply,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.80,0:52:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,癌症和出生缺陷率急剧上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a steep increase in the rates of cancer and birth defects.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.84,0:52:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道具体的死亡数量  但肯定会很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know how many deaths there will be, but many.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.30,0:52:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于白俄罗斯和乌克兰来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For Byelorussia and the Ukraine,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.06,0:52:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影响意味着该地区至少一百年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"impact" means completely uninhabitable
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.64,0:52:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不适合人类居住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for a minimum of 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.98,0:52:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有超过五千万人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are more than 50 million people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.40,0:52:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住在白俄罗斯和乌克兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}living in Byelorussia and Ukraine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.24,0:52:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六千万人  是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sixty, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.45,0:52:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有多少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And how long before this happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.71,0:52:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约48到72小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Approximately 48 to 72 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.05,0:53:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们也许有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we may have a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.42,0:53:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能抽出水箱中的水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can pump the water from the tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.09,0:53:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是水箱被阀门封死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Unfortunately, the tanks are sealed shut by a sluice gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.47,0:53:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能从管道系统内部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the gate can only be opened manually
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.51,0:53:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手动开启\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from within the duct system itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.31,0:53:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们需要三名工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So we need to find three plant workers
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.52,0:53:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解工厂内部的工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who know the facility well enough
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.02,0:53:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入地下区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to enter the basement here,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.94,0:53:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺着管道系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}find their way through all these duct ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.36,0:53:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这边的阀门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}get to the sluice gate valve here,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.45,0:53:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好让我们抽干水箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and give us the access we need to pump out the tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.95,0:53:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  我们还需要你的允许\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course, we will need your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.95,0:53:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的什么允许\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My permission for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.62,0:53:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管道中的水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, the water in these ducts,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.63,0:53:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,污染等级很高...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the level of radioactive contamination--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.34,0:53:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很可能一周后就会死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll likely be dead in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.67,0:53:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要你的允许  杀死三个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're asking for your permission to kill three men.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.06,0:54:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrade Legasov...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.52,0:54:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有胜利都有不可避免的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all victories inevitably come at a cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.46,0:54:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord1\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur8\fad(0,0)\pos(191.2,67.2)}4月28日  上午9点30分\N\N\N\N\N{\fs20}爆炸发生56小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.53,0:55:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后打开这里的...水阀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And open the sluice gate valve... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.37,0:55:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水阀很难操作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The valve will be difficult to operate,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.37,0:55:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们需要三名工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so we'll need three men
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.16,0:55:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟知地下区域构造的工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who will need to know the basement layout.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.17,0:55:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  自愿的人会有重赏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, of course, any volunteers will be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.50,0:55:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年四百卢布的津贴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A yearly stipend of 400 rubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.68,0:56:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是本来就在一号和二号反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, uh, for those of you working in reactors
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.43,0:56:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作的人  还能得到提拔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one and two, promotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.89,0:56:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一号和二号反应堆还在工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why are reactors one and two still operating at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.94,0:56:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友是那晚的保安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My friend was a security guard that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.65,0:56:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, uh, she's now dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.78,0:56:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也都听说了那些消防员的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we've all heard about the firemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.28,0:56:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你要我们游到一个燃烧着的反应堆下方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now you want us to swim underneath a burning reactor?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.74,0:56:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道污染有多重吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you even know how contaminated it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.20,0:56:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我给不出具体的数字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I... I don't have an exact number.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.04,0:56:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要具体数字也知道这会要了我们的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't need an exact number to know if it'll kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.42,0:56:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你甚至都不敢告诉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you can't even tell us that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.88,0:56:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为什么要这么做  为了四百卢布吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why should we do this? For what, 400 rubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.76,0:56:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要这么做是因为别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll do it because it must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.93,0:56:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为其他人都做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you'll do it, because nobody else can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.61,0:56:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则会有上百万人死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if you don't, millions will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.49,0:56:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们说这个理由还不够  我不信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you tell me that's not enough, I won't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.70,0:57:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们民族一向不同于其他人的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is what has always set our people apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.79,0:57:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们血液中流淌千年的牺牲精神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A thousand years of sacrifice in our veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.79,0:57:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一代人必须面对他们的苦难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And every generation must know its own suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.59,0:57:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唾弃这起事故的元凶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I spit on the people who did this,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.46,0:57:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我诅咒我需要付出的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I curse the price I have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.39,0:57:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在接受事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I'm making my peace with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.93,0:57:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在轮到你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and now you make yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.10,0:57:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游到那水下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And go into that water.
